# Global git attributes (core.attributesFile → ~/.gitconfig).
#
# mergiraf: AST-aware merge driver defined in ~/.gitconfig ([merge "mergiraf"]).
# `* merge=mergiraf` routes every merge through mergiraf; it detects the file's
# language and resolves structurally, delegating to git's default merge for any
# file type it doesn't support. Regenerate the explicit language list any time
# with `mergiraf languages --gitattributes`. https://mergiraf.org/
* merge=mergiraf
